href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 26, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104hnh1665702759840.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hnh1665702759840.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hnh1665702759840.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"hnh1665702759840\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Operation activated by the SAX parser when it issues a non-recoverable\n    error.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104hnh1665702759840_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"hnh1665702759840__codeblock_cgw_qc4_hwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation FATALERROR\nparams\n     string List: in\n  endparams\n\nImplement your code here\n\nend; FATALERROR operation</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hnh1665702759840__section_krb_sc4_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1008241e53\">Parameters</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl\" id=\"hnh1665702759840__dl_ikf_cc4_hwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">List</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd\">Associated list identifying the location and nature of the error. The identifiers can\n              be:<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"hnh1665702759840__ul_jwl_cc4_hwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hnh1665702759840__li_d48380e1_d48381e1_d48382e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">LINE</code>—line number within the\n                XML document where the error occurred</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hnh1665702759840__li_d48383e1_d48384e1_d48385e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">COLUMN</code>—column number within\n                the XML document where the error occurred</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hnh1665702759840__li_d48386e1_d48387e1_d48388e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">MESSAGE</code>—error message issued\n                by the parser. If provided by the SAX parser, the following may also be in the list:\n                  <ul class=\"ul\" id=\"hnh1665702759840__ul_kwl_cc4_hwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hnh1665702759840__li_d48389e1_d48390e1_d48391e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">PUBLICID</code>—public identifier\n                    of an XML entity</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hnh1665702759840__li_d48392e1_d48393e1_d48394e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">SYSTEMID</code>—local identifier\n                    of an XML entity</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul></dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hnh1665702759840__section_glj_dd4_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1008241e102\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hnh1665702759840__p_d137117e1_d137118e1_d137119e1\">After issuing a fatal error, no other operation of the\n        handler instance will be activated. Instead, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">PARSE</span> and\n          <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">PARSEFILE</span> return with a negative value.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hnh1665702759840__p_d137120e1_d137121e1_d137122e1\">If <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">FATALERROR</span> returns a negative\n        value, this value is returned by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">PARSE</span> and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">PARSEFILE</span>.\n        Otherwise, they return error <code class=\"ph codeph\">-151, &lt;UACTERR_EXCEPTION_THROWN&gt;</code>.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kch1665703202145.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>PARSE</a><p>Parses a specified XML stream.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ttv1665703202809.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>PARSEFILE</a><p>Parses an XML document in the specified file.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528296\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528296\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "FATALERROR Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 26, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Operation activated by the SAX parser when it issues a non-recoverable error. Explain this code operation FATALERROR params string List: in endparams Implement your code here end; FATALERROR operation Copy Parameters List Associated list identifying the location and nature of the error. The identifiers can be: LINE —line number within the XML document where the error occurred COLUMN —column number within the XML document where the error occurred MESSAGE —error message issued by the parser. If provided by the SAX parser, the following may also be in the list: PUBLICID —public identifier of an XML entity SYSTEMID —local identifier of an XML entity Description After issuing a fatal error, no other operation of the handler instance will be activated. Instead, PARSE and PARSEFILE return with a negative value. If FATALERROR returns a negative value, this value is returned by PARSE and PARSEFILE . Otherwise, they return error -151, <UACTERR_EXCEPTION_THROWN> . Related Links PARSE Parses a specified XML stream. PARSEFILE Parses an XML document in the specified file. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}